вҹҰ Test Unicode operators in typechecker вҹ§

e console

О»boolText(value:рқ”№)вҶ’рқ•Ҡ match value{
  trueвҶ’"true"|
  falseвҶ’"false"
}

О»main()вҶ’рқ•Ң=console.log(
  "All tests passed: "
  ++boolText(testLe(5,10))
  ++", "
  ++boolText(testGe(10,5))
  ++", "
  ++boolText(testNe(5,10))
  ++", "
  ++boolText(В¬testAnd(true,false))
  ++", "
  ++boolText(testOr(true,false))
)

вҹҰ Test and / or вҹ§
О»testAnd(a:рқ”№,b:рқ”№)вҶ’рқ”№=a and b

вҹҰ Test вүӨ and вүҘ вҹ§
О»testGe(a:в„Ө,b:в„Ө)вҶ’рқ”№=aвүҘb
О»testLe(a:в„Ө,b:в„Ө)вҶ’рқ”№=aвүӨb

вҹҰ Test вү  вҹ§
О»testNe(a:в„Ө,b:в„Ө)вҶ’рқ”№=aвү b

вҹҰ Test and / or вҹ§
О»testOr(a:рқ”№,b:рқ”№)вҶ’рқ”№=a or b
